            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Attributable actions (user/role traceability)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Publication timestamps and historical states</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-4"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Exportable snapshots for internal sign-off</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-emerald-100/30 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-3">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-bl-full translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:translate-x-12 group-hover:-translate-y-12 transition-transform" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-deco-3"></div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-icon-3">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-h-3">Auditor Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-p-3">Compliance teams should not assemble proof packs. They should grant access. All access is Read-only, Scoped, and Logged.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-list-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Inspect passports and version history</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Review readiness state and completeness</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Validate safety notices and publication windows</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-4"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Verify lifecycle events relevant to compliance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visual Separator Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-950 text-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-bg">
      <img crossorigin="anonymous"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1200&q=80"
        srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
        sizes="100vw"
        alt="Security and Governance" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-img" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950 via-slate-950/80 to-transparent" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-container">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-content">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-title">Staying aligned as requirements evolve.</h2>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-grid">
           <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-box">
             <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-label-wrap">
               <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-icon-box">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield-check"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
               </div>
               <h4 class="text-emerald-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-label">Stable Foundation</h4>
             </div>
             <p class="text-slate-300 font-medium mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:ehc187">What stays stable:</p>
             <ul class="space-y-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-list">
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-li-1">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-dot-1"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-txt-1">The identity model</span>
               </li>
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-li-2">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-dot-2"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-txt-2">The governance model</span>
               </li>
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-li-3">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-dot-3"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-txt-3">The evidence model</span>
               </li>
             </ul>
           </div>
           <div class="flex flex-col justify-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-text">
             <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-h3">Adapting to Mandates</h3>
             <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-p">
               Delegated acts mature over time. TieBack is designed so your operating model stays stable while requirements change. What adapts is simply the field enforcement rules per category and market.
             </p>
             <div class="flex items-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-stats">
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-1">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-400" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-val-1">Adaptable</div>
                  <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-lbl-1">Field Enforcement</div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/10" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-sep"></div>
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-2">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-400" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-val-2">Stable</div>
                  <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-lbl-2">Operating Model</div>
                </div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Final CTA -->
  <section id="request-access" class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-50/50 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-grad"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-content">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-h">Confidence that passports <span class="text-emerald-700" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-emerald">remain correct.</span></h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-p">
          Early preparation without premature burden. Clear accountability across teams. Audit-ready evidence without manual work.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-buttons">
          <a href="/platform/why-tieback/" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl shadow-emerald-200 hover:-translate-y-1 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-secondary">
            Digital Product Passport Overview
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
---
import BaseLayout depuis &#x27;@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro&#x27;;
import { SITE } depuis &#x27;@/config/site&#x27;;

const title = &quot;Préparation à la conformité — TieBack&quot;;
const description = &quot;Préparez-vous à l&#x27;avance sans aller trop loin. TieBack offre aux équipes chargées de la conformité, des affaires juridiques et des produits une méthode structurée pour modéliser les exigences en matière d&#x27;DPP, effectuer des contrôles de préparation et conserver des preuves prêtes pour un audit.&quot;;
---

<baselayout title="&lt;astro-expr" id="1">
  description={description}
  &gt;
  <!-- 1. Use Case Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-52 md:pb-40 overflow-hidden bg-white" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:hero">
    <!-- Subtle Background Accents -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-7xl pointer-events-none" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bg-accents">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] rounded-full bg-emerald-50/50 blur-[120px]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:accent-1"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[30%] h-[30%] rounded-full bg-slate-50 blur-[100px]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:accent-2"></div>
    </div></section></baselayout>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:hero-container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:hero-content">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 py-1 px-3 mb-8 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest text-emerald-700 uppercase bg-emerald-50/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-emerald-100 rounded-full" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:eyebrow">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 animate-pulse" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:pulse"></span>
          Cas n° 4
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-[1.05]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:title">
        
          <span class="text-emerald-700" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:title-emerald">Préparation</span>
        à la conformité
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:subtext">
          Préparez-vous à l&#x27;avance sans aller trop loin. TieBack offre aux équipes chargées de la conformité, des affaires juridiques et des produits une méthode structurée pour modéliser les exigences du Digital Product Passport, effectuer des contrôles de préparation et conserver des preuves prêtes pour un audit à mesure que les règles évoluent.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-5" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:buttons">
          <a href="#request-access" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl shadow-emerald-200 hover:-translate-y-1" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:btn-primary">
            Préparez votre équipe
          </a>
          
          <a href="/platform/why-tieback/" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-slate-300" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:btn-secondary">
            Présentation de la plateforme
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  

  <!-- 2. The Challenge -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200/60 relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-grid">
        <div class="relative" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-left">
          <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-24 h-24 bg-emerald-100/50 rounded-full blur-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:accent-3"></div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-[1.15] relative" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-heading">
            Conçu pour les responsables de programmes qui ont besoin <span class="italic font-serif text-emerald-700" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-emerald">d&#x27;un contrôle serein</span> — sur l&#x27;ensemble des marchés, des catégories et face au changement.
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1 gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-list">
             <div class="flex gap-4 items-center group bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 transition-all hover:border-emerald-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-50" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-item-1">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-emerald-700 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-icon-1">01</div>
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-text-1">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-h-1">Préparez-vous avant l&#x27;entrée en vigueur des obligations</h4>
                </div>
             </div>
             <div class="flex gap-4 items-center group bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 transition-all hover:border-emerald-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-50" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-item-2">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-emerald-700 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-icon-2">02</div>
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-text-2">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-h-2">Génération automatique de preuves et de rapports d&#x27;audit</h4>
                </div>
             </div>
             <div class="flex gap-4 items-center group bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 transition-all hover:border-emerald-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-50" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-item-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-emerald-700 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-icon-3">03</div>
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-text-3">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-h-3">Les rôles de gouvernance réduisent les coûts liés à la conformité</h4>
                </div>
             </div>
             <div class="flex gap-4 items-center group bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 transition-all hover:border-emerald-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-50" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-item-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-emerald-700 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-icon-4">04</div>
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-text-4">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-h-4">Restez en phase avec l&#x27;évolution des exigences</h4>
                </div>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-right">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-box">
            <h3 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-700 font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:reality-eyebrow">La réalité de la conformité</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-800 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-quote">
              Les programmes de passeport numérique des produits introduisent une dimension permanente. Les informations sur les produits doivent rester structurées, à jour et vérifiables au fil du temps — et la charge de la preuve incombe à l&#x27;organisation qui met les produits sur le marché de l&#x27;UE.
            </p>
            <div class="h-px bg-slate-100 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-divider"></div>
            <div class="grid gap-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-bullets">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-bullet-1">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 mt-2 shrink-0" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-dot-1"></span>
                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-text-1">Les exigences évoluent catégorie par catégorie</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-bullet-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 mt-2 shrink-0" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-dot-2"></span>
                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-text-2">Les preuves sont obligatoires, et non facultatives</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-bullet-3">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 mt-2 shrink-0" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-dot-3"></span>
                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-text-3">Plusieurs équipes contribuent à la même fiche de passeport</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:challenge-bullet-4">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 mt-2 shrink-0" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-dot-4"></span>
                <p class="text-slate-900 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:bullet-text-4">Le plus difficile, c&#x27;est la continuité : maintenir l&#x27;exactitude des passeports au fil du temps</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Capabilities Grid -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:capabilities">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:capabilities-container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-20" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:capabilities-header">
        <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs block mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-label">Phase préalable au mandat</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-title">Mode de référence.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xl leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-subtext">Les structures de passeport sont disponibles, les champs sont visibles et les équipes peuvent harmoniser les sources de données, les contributions des fournisseurs et la responsabilité interne sans perturber les opérations.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-grid">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-emerald-100/30 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-1">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-bl-full translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:translate-x-12 group-hover:-translate-y-12 transition-transform" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-deco-1"></div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-icon-1">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-h-1">Ce que permet l&#x27;TieBack</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-p-1">Construisez vos bases en toute sécurité avant que les délais réglementaires ne vous obligent à mettre en œuvre des solutions à la hâte.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-list-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-1-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Structures de référence appliquées de manière cohérente au niveau des références</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-1-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Séparation claire entre les champs recommandés et les champs obligatoires</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-1-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Historique des versions dès le premier jour</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-1-4"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Présentation adaptée au marché</li>
          </ul>
        </div></div></div></section>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-emerald-100/30 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-2">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-bl-full translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:translate-x-12 group-hover:-translate-y-12 transition-transform" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-deco-2"></div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-icon-2">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-h-2">Gouvernance et données factuelles</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-p-2">La préparation devient mesurable lorsque les données sont générées automatiquement.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-list-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Passeports versionnés (ce qui a changé, quand, par qui)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Actions attribuables (traçabilité utilisateur/rôle)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Horodatage des publications et historique des états</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-2-4"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Instantanés exportables pour validation interne</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-emerald-100/30 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-3">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-bl-full translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:translate-x-12 group-hover:-translate-y-12 transition-transform" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-card-deco-3"></div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-icon-3">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-h-3">Expérience des auditeurs</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-p-3">Les équipes chargées de la conformité ne doivent pas constituer de dossiers de preuves. Elles doivent accorder des droits d&#x27;accès. Tous les accès sont en lecture seule, limités à un périmètre précis et consignés.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-list-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Vérifier les passeports et l&#x27;historique des versions</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Vérifier l&#x27;état de préparation et l&#x27;exhaustivité</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Valider les avis de sécurité et les fenêtres de publication</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cap-li-3-4"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Vérifier les événements du cycle de vie pertinents pour la conformité</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      
    
  

  <!-- Visual Separator Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-950 text-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-bg">
      <img crossorigin="anonymous"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1200&q=80"
        srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639503547276-90230c4a4198?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
        sizes="100vw"
        alt="Security and Governance" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-img" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950 via-slate-950/80 to-transparent" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-container">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-content">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-title">S&#x27;adapter à l&#x27;évolution des besoins.</h2>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-grid">
           <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-box">
             <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-label-wrap">
               <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-icon-box">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield-check"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
               </div>
               <h4 class="text-emerald-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-label">Des bases solides</h4>
             </div>
             <p class="text-slate-300 font-medium mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:ehc187">Ce qui reste stable :</p>
             <ul class="space-y-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-list">
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-li-1">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-dot-1"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-txt-1">Le modèle d&#x27;identité</span>
               </li>
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-li-2">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-dot-2"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-txt-2">Le modèle de gouvernance</span>
               </li>
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-li-3">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-dot-3"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-txt-3">Le modèle de preuves</span>
               </li>
             </ul>
           </div>
           <div class="flex flex-col justify-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-text">
             <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-h3">Adaptation aux mandats</h3>
             <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-p">
               Les actes délégués évoluent avec le temps. TieBack est conçu pour que votre modèle opérationnel reste stable tandis que les exigences changent. Ce qui s&#x27;adapte, ce sont simplement les règles d&#x27;application sur le terrain par catégorie et par marché.
             </p>
             <div class="flex items-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:evidence-stats">
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-1">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-400" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-val-1">Adaptable</div>
                  <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-lbl-1">Application sur le terrain</div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/10" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-sep"></div>
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-2">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-400" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-val-2">Stable</div>
                  <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:stat-lbl-2">Modèle opérationnel</div>
                </div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Final CTA -->
  <section id="request-access" class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-50/50 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-grad"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/eu-dpp.astro:cta-container">
